## Create image — admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/images
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
    "id_product": 11,
    "image_url": "https://example.com/apd-vol1.jpg",
    "is_cover": false
}

### Response
// {"status":"success","code":201,"msg":"ProductImage created successfully","data":{"id":12},"timestamp":"2026-03-15 03:10:09"}


## Create second image — admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/images
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
    "id_product": 11,
    "image_url": "https://example.com/apd-vol1-back.jpg",
    "is_cover": false
}

### Response
// {"status":"success","code":201,"msg":"ProductImage created successfully","data":{"id":13},"timestamp":"2026-03-15 03:10:31"}


## Update image — admin
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/images/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
    "is_cover": true
}

### Response
// {"status":"success","code":200,"msg":"ProductImage updated successfully","data":null,"timestamp":"2026-03-15 03:10:46"}


## Delete image — admin
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/images/11
Accept: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Response
// {"status":"error","code":404,"msg":"ProductImage not found","data":null,"timestamp":"2026-03-15 03:10:54"}


## Create — Fail (product not found)
POST {{baseUrl}}/images
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
    "id_product": 999,
    "image_url": "https://example.com/test.jpg"
}

### Response
// {"status":"error","code":404,"msg":"Product not found","data":null,"timestamp":"2026-03-15 03:11:12"}

